一站的日期和站点，巡演首站定于今年 8 月开始，并将在今年剩余时间持续到 2025 年，在新加坡、日本、印度尼西亚等地进行演出。</p><h2>明天X一起</h2><figure id="attachment_3766773" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3766773" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3766773" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us.jpg" alt="txt hyperfocus 虚拟现实音乐会 我们明天 x 一起" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/txt-hyperfocus-virtual-reality-concert-us-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3766773" class="wp-caption-text"> TXT。图片来源：朝鲜日报 JNS/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>《行动：承诺》EP。 2 世界巡演 – 仁川</strong></p><p><strong>2025 年 3 月</strong><br />周五 7 日至周日 9 日 – 韩国仁川 Inspire Arena</p><p> Big Hit Music 五重奏将从三月份宣布的休息中回归，举办三晚安可音乐会，庆祝他们庞大的世界巡演“Act: Promise”的结束。 3 月 8 日的音乐会在 Inspire Arena 举行，国际歌迷也可以在线直播。</p><h2>纳米混合X </h2><figure id="attachment_3760720" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760720" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760720" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty.jpg" alt="nmixx 病毒式上演音频故障" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-v